comments: The strategy i used was to first focus on one letter in my case the last one and then once i had those memorised go to another so that the chances of getting it wrong would be lower, so i associated the last letter to each object, finding out there are matches of two with the same last letter :) thank you for letting me participate i very much enjoyed the challenge, i believe this last part was easier for me since i struggle more with long term memory so on the first ones once we got to the guessing part i had already forgotten the first image
